19s spokesperson Taranath Adhikari shared that the anti-graft body has demanded punishment against Das as per the Anti-corruption act along with confiscation of his illegally earned properties.","title":"CIAA files graft case at Special Court against ex-VC Das - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2020/15/127798/","video":[]}
